153
00:11:57,016 --> 00:12:00,008
- How much do you want to put on it?
- Everything I got left.

154
00:12:00,086 --> 00:12:03,283
- 70,000 francs.
- Bob, you're crazy. What if you lose?

155
00:12:03,355 --> 00:12:06,950
I'll have hit rock-bottom.
I'll have to change my ways.

156
00:12:07,026 --> 00:12:08,960
- Place it for me.
- Do it yourself.

157
00:12:09,028 --> 00:12:12,759
Me? Place a bet
like that? Never.

158
00:12:12,832 --> 00:12:15,232
[Hooves Clattering]

159
00:12:16,936 --> 00:12:18,927
