[Cries Out]

169
00:12:43,362 --> 00:12:47,822
- [Whinnies]
- [Grunts, Screams]

170
00:12:47,900 --> 00:12:50,368
- [Men Shouting, Horse Neighing]
- Think it'll make the race?

171
00:12:53,272 --> 00:12:56,469
Why does he have
so much ice cream?

172
00:12:56,542 --> 00:12:59,067
That's all
he can eat sometimes.

173
00:12:59,145 --> 00:13:01,875
