186
00:14:23,627 --> 00:14:25,618
- Okay.
- [Grunts]

187
00:14:27,698 --> 00:14:30,462
- So. Where to, boss?
- Home.

188
00:14:30,534 --> 00:14:32,627
Don't you want to continue
your winning streak?

189
00:14:32,703 --> 00:14:35,194
- [Snorts]
- [Chuckles]

190
00:14:50,154 --> 00:14:54,853
- What happened to home?
- Forget about home.
You're going to Monte Carlo.

191
00:14:54,925 --> 00:14:57,519
- Where in Monte Carlo?
- The Casino Riviera.

192
00:14:57,595 --> 00:15:02,658
- [Groans]
- You see, Bob, I figure
you needed a reason for living.

193
00:15:02,733 --> 00:15:05,327
- Now that your luck's bottomed out.
- That it has.

194
00:15:05,402 --> 00:15:07,870
- The Casino Riviera...
- Has a safe.

195
