that has a happy ending.

1098
01:25:54,509 --> 01:25:56,443
- She died?
- Uh-huh.

1099
01:26:11,826 --> 01:26:13,817
Anne.

1100
01:26:20,301 --> 01:26:22,235
You're gonna see
fake glamor...

1101
01:26:22,303 --> 01:26:25,932
serious money, and a lot
