[Whispers, Indistinct]

1225
01:40:18,637 --> 01:40:20,571
The safe is empty.

1226
01:40:55,541 --> 01:40:59,102
- [Hangs Up Telephone]
- I could accept a post-dated check.

1227
01:40:59,178 --> 01:41:03,581
- Tell him again, will you?
- Well, it seems someone cracked the safe.

1228
01:41:03,649 --> 01:41:06,015
Tell him, hey, of all nights,
just my luck.

1229
01:41:06,085 --> 01:41:09,145
- And I am awaiting legal advice.
- How long must we wait?

1230
01:41:09,221 --> 01:41:12,315
- I have a meeting in Paris.
- Shall we speed things up and arrest you now?

1231
01:41:12,391 --> 01:41:15,485
- Me? On what charges?
- Criminal conspiracy.

1232
01:41:15,561 --> 01:41:19,327
- [Roger] Criminal conspiracy
can be hard to prove.
- Impossible in my case.

1233
01:41:19,398 --> 01:41:21,866
I've been here all evening.
Look at that crowd.

1234
01:41:21,934 --> 01:41:26,268
